definitions.definition: Someone who is just starting at something, or has only recently started.
examples: I'm new to learning Finnish: I'm just a beginner .

definitions.definition: Someone who sets something in motion.
examples: The beginner of the games lit the ceremonial torch.

definitions.definition: An actor who is present on stage in the first moments of a play .

main_definition: Someone who is just starting at something, or has only recently started.
secondary_definitions: Someone who sets something in motion.
( theater ) An actor who is present on stage in the first moments of a play .
